item.title: Events
item.description: Upcomming events Black Tie Builders Awards Dinner 2020 The Builders formal dinner and awards ceremony will be held at the sophisticated Newtown sport Bar this year where cocktail samosas and Waitako will flow into the night. The prime minister will be handing out awards for excellence in the fields of; coping artistry, bricklaying finesse and finishing prowess. At the end of the night the much sought after golden trowel will be awarded to the Builder of The Year.
